Lingua-EN-WSD-CorpusBased version 0.10
======================================

This module is the implementation of a simple approach to 
word sense disambiguation. It uses a (domain) corpus to find
the best fitting sense out of the WordNet senses. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  WordNet::QueryData
  WordNet::Similarity (for the stemming)
  String::Util

